## Category Guide

| Category | What It Means |
|----------|---------------|
| **feature** | Enhancement to an existing project |
| **project** | New standalone project |
| **experiment** | Technical exploration or proof-of-concept |
| **tool** | Developer tooling or automation |
| **content** | Blog post, video, documentation |
| **business** | Revenue opportunity or venture |

